msgid "WhatsApp Must Act to Protect Elections"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Mozilla is making an urgent call for WhatsApp to implement three simple changes in its product to slow the spread of political disinformation and other harmful content on its platform."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "title"
msgid "WhatsApp Must Act to Protect Elections"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.2723816b-7394-42ea-b13e-b47260d439d0"
msgid ""
"Elections for about half the world’s population take place in 2024. <b>But</b> <b>the integrity of these elections could be under threat, because WhatsApp isn’t doing enough to detect and stop "
"networked hate speech, disinformation, and political violence</b> <b>on its platform.</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.2723816b-7394-42ea-b13e-b47260d439d0"
msgid ""
"Mozilla is making an urgent call for WhatsApp to implement three simple changes in its product to slow the spread of political disinformation and other harmful content on its platform. <b>Will you "
"add your name to ask WhatsApp to update its product to protect global elections?</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9369e272-4333-45ad-84ba-ab53d7a83975.accordion_items.39013836-39e2-443d-b203-578450d5bfa4.title"
msgid "Read Our Message to WhatsApp:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9369e272-4333-45ad-84ba-ab53d7a83975.accordion_items.39013836-39e2-443d-b203-578450d5bfa4.content.42859f29-ef40-4033-a608-84f0e323289e"
msgid "To WhatsApp:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9369e272-4333-45ad-84ba-ab53d7a83975.accordion_items.39013836-39e2-443d-b203-578450d5bfa4.content.42859f29-ef40-4033-a608-84f0e323289e"
msgid "WhatsApp needs to implement these product changes during polling days and in the month before and the month after elections:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9369e272-4333-45ad-84ba-ab53d7a83975.accordion_items.39013836-39e2-443d-b203-578450d5bfa4.content.42859f29-ef40-4033-a608-84f0e323289e"
msgid ""
"<b>Add friction to forwarding messages:</b> Reduce the ease with which messages can be forwarded on the platform by adding one additional step which nudges users to pause and reflect before they "
"forward content."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9369e272-4333-45ad-84ba-ab53d7a83975.accordion_items.39013836-39e2-443d-b203-578450d5bfa4.content.42859f29-ef40-4033-a608-84f0e323289e"
msgid ""
"<b>Add disinformation warning labels to viral content:</b> Automatically add clear “Highly forwarded: please verify” warning labels to viral messages, in addition to the “forwarded many times” label"
" currently in use."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9369e272-4333-45ad-84ba-ab53d7a83975.accordion_items.39013836-39e2-443d-b203-578450d5bfa4.content.42859f29-ef40-4033-a608-84f0e323289e"
msgid "<b>Reduce WhatsApp’s broadcast capabilities</b>: Disable the Communities feature and also limit the size of broadcast lists to 50 people and cap their usage to twice a day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.9369e272-4333-45ad-84ba-ab53d7a83975.accordion_items.39013836-39e2-443d-b203-578450d5bfa4.content.42859f29-ef40-4033-a608-84f0e323289e"
msgid ""
"Without decisive action from WhatsApp, disinformation attacks will likely scale up in 2024, aimed at manipulating and undermining elections affecting half of the world’s population. WhatsApp must "
"act to change its product to protect election integrity."
msgstr ""

